	+e.section
		+section({
			header: {
				title: {
					tag: 'h1',
					text: 'Training videos',
					attr: {
						class: '_size_h1 _case_normal'
					}
				}
			}
		})
			+e.content
				.page__container
					+e.text._size_m._width_l
						p Uncover the secrets to creating stunning looks with Concept products!
						p The brand's library features recommendations on coloring, lightening, hair care, and special treatments that will help stylists become high-level colorists. In the free training videos, you will learn how to work with modern hairdressing products and how to properly address issues with problematic or damaged hair.

